data.description: Cut the commute and appreciate being only 5 minutes to Hurlburt Field's front gate! Have peace of mind with a 2018 roof, 2018 HVAC, 2016 water heater, AND enjoy utility savings with fully paid off solar panels (an over $31,000 value)! The kitchen has been previously renovated with new cabinets, granite countertops, and brushed nickel hardware, fixtures, and lighting. There is a nice sized living room with laminate flooring which is open to the eat in kitchen area with french doors leading to the fully fenced in backyard. Back inside the master bedroom has two great sized closets with a bathroom featuring an extended double vanity space. The other two bedrooms are located down the same hallway with ample closet space and a shared updated guest bathroom with granite vanity. No HOA!
